CatDescriptText: Portion of related article in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 7, 1945, pg. 16, reads: "Grays, Yanks Play Here Next Tuesday - New York Black Yankees will oppose Homestead Grays on Tuesday, July 10th at Forbes Field.  This will be the second appearance of the New Yorkers this season but the first time to play under the beautiful Forbes Field lighting system..."
TitMainTitle: Homestead Grays baseball player sliding into third base, with two infielders possibly New York Black Yankees nearby, during night game at Forbes Field
